%---------------------------------
% ABSTRACT
%---------------------------------

\chapter*{\centering ABSTRACT}
\addcontentsline{toc}{chapter}{ABSTRACT}

Yoga plays an important role in maintaining physical and mental well-being.
However performing yoga poses incorrectly may lead to injuries. The proposed
system "AsanaFix: AI Based Yoga Posture Assistant" uses computer vision and
machine learning techniques to detect and correct yoga postures in real time.

The system analyzes body key points and compares them with ideal yoga poses
to provide feedback to users.

