%---------------------------------
% CHAPTER 1
%---------------------------------

\chapter{Introduction}

\section{Introduction to the Project}

Yoga is a physical, mental, and spiritual practice that originated in India.
Maintaining correct posture during yoga practice is very important to gain
maximum health benefits and avoid injuries.

\section{Existing System}

Traditional yoga training requires direct supervision from trained instructors.
However, many beginners practice yoga without guidance which leads to incorrect
postures.

\section{Proposed System}

The proposed system uses artificial intelligence and computer vision techniques
to analyze the user's body posture and provide feedback in real time.

\section{Scope of the Project}

The system helps beginners practice yoga safely by detecting posture errors
and suggesting corrections.

\section{Objectives of the Project}

The main objective of this project is to design an AI-based yoga posture
assistant that helps users perform yoga poses correctly.

\section{Organization of the Report}

This report is organized into different chapters describing system analysis,
design, implementation, results, and conclusions.

