% CHAPTER 2
%---------------------------------

\chapter{Literature Survey}

\section{Summary of Literature Survey}

Many researchers have explored computer vision techniques for posture
recognition. Deep learning and pose estimation models such as OpenPose
and MediaPipe are widely used.

